articles.title: Nord Stream pipelines: Ukrainian government denies involvement in sabotage - CNN
articles.description: Ukraine has denied any involvement in the sabotage of the Nord Stream pipelines following a media report citing new intelligence that a "pro-Ukrainian group" may have been behind last year's attack targeting Russia's gas deliveries to Europe.

articles.title: Why Valentine’s Day is trending on Holi - The Economic Times
